{"tid":1492501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"勇武再一次淪為condom","createTime":"2019-08-21T00:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:14:16.000Z","uid":61520,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"786e5157d4ea253838dc24e84213ba66e4ebbd55","tid":1492501,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5BM97j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5BM97j.png&h=fa62b179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林莫求其督兩年散仔出黎，告條最多坐三年既傷人<br />\n<br />\n成班就唔記得哂死線，又話818係幫手話比人知和平冇用，要行動升級<br />\n<br />\n出面熱門唔係咩高志森比人封、藍絲冇聲出既圍爐post，就係we connet圍中國，日本出片撐香港既飛機post<br />\n<br />\n最切身既行動post就得一兩個<br />\n<br />\n唔設死線，唔大力宣傳死線比全世界知，我地點名正言順行動升級<br />\n<br />\n818就講到點重要，唔出黎枉為人<br />\n<br />\nFollow up既野就wfc，繼續拎人數打飛機<br />\n<br />\n818勇武比足面和理非，而家要back up冇人理？<br />\n<br />\n時間無多，大家將條死線spread出去好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人唔係文宣組，見死線冇人理，只係夾硬用word谷張爛鳩圖出黎<br />\n<br />\n張圖係好撚核突嫁啦，嫌棄既就麻煩幫手整張靚既"},{"pid":"9ece47be4a9d6d20a786435d8e35c47faad5a293","tid":1492501,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"屬於香港既#metoo行動上線啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dHeBkS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dHeBkS</a><br />\n<br />\n比人無理對待?#metoo啦<br />\n比警察當你係狗?#metoo啦<br />\n比chinazi當你二等公民?#metoo啦<br />\n<br />\n屬於香港既#metoo行動 正式上線"},{"pid":"0626ee59391316818737fa3fd88b2c38210337bf","tid":1492501,"uid":185085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDDzDzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDDzDzb.jpg&h=a26a19d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f87f40aa2de58e13367a9c01feaee937c4bf854","tid":1492501,"uid":277816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span s